title._content: Mansard Style House in Keene New Hampshire

description._content: TITLE Mansard Style House in Keene New Hampshire CREATOR Wardwell, Anne, Keene NH SUBJECT Houses - NH - Keene DESCRIPTION "Excellent examples of a variety of architectural styles are evident. Many, such as this, are in good and original condition, but some are sadly altered, thus detracting from the quality of the street. Finally, the sheer width of the street precludes the intimate neighborhood character present on Court Street." PUBLISHER Keene Public Library and the Historical Society of Cheshire County DATE DIGITAL 20090312 DATE ORIGINAL 1975 RESOURCE TYPE slides FORMAT image/jpg RESOURCE IDENTIFIER hsykfok072 RIGHTS MANAGMENT No known copyright restrictions.
